snippet.title: Athenian Rhapsody - Official Asmongold Limited Time Event Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Athenian Rhapsody is an adventure RPG developed by Nico Papalia. Players will be able to encounter and team up with content creator Asmongold in a limited-time event by traveling to a faraway island. Athenian Rhapsody is available now for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and PC.

#Gaming #Games #GameTrailers
